Package: scenic
Title: Simulation and Causal Estimation for Negative Control Inference
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Charis", "Xiong", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "charis.xiong@gmail.com")
Description: Provides functions for simulating data under a causal model with
    unmeasured confounding, and for running four causal inference estimators:
    DIRECT (OLS with controls), COCA (negative-control outcome correction),
    IV2SLS (two-stage least squares), and PGC (proxy-based G-component
    correction). Includes parallelized simulation sweeps across parameter grids.
